You know, this is, you know, a Nita cell, which, you know, is our exciting hope for a car that is maybe going to have the horsepower of Carvicti, but with sort of better handling and sort of reliability on the open road.

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:20.920
And I'm going to be presenting cleanest slides.

